ki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9780203829615\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9780203829615\">9780203829615</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Marx+and+Education+%28Routledge+Key+Ideas+in+Education%29&amp;rft.place=Routledge%2C+New+York&amp;rft.date=2011&amp;rft.isbn=9780203829615&amp;rft.aulast=Anyon&amp;rft.aufirst=Jean&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJean+Anyon\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Literacy-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-Literacy_6-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation book\">Finn, Patrick J. (2009). <i>Literacy with an Attitude</i>. Albany: State University of New York Press. <a href=\"/wiki/International_Standard_Book_Number\" title=\"International Standard Book Number\">ISBN</a>&#160;<a href=\"/wiki/Special:BookSources/9781438428062\" title=\"Special:BookSources/9781438428062\">9781438428062</a>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Literacy+with+an+Attitude&amp;rft.place=Albany&amp;rft.pub=State+University+of+New+York+Press&amp;rft.date=2009&amp;rft.isbn=9781438428062&amp;rft.aulast=Finn&amp;rft.aufirst=Patrick+J.&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AJean+Anyon\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-7\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-7\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation web\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://craigcunningham.com/nlu/fnd504/anyon.htm\">\"Welcome to Craig A. Cunningham's Web Site\"</a>. <i>craigcunningham.com</i><span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Ret